Thank you, here will do.

284
00:21:52,720 --> 00:21:53,800
Take a look.

285
00:21:54,599 --> 00:21:56,880
Va_y, il est des nôtres.

286
00:21:59,680 --> 00:22:03,480
In the pile, there is season 5
of The Walking Dead.

